Name: Average time from 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' to 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Average time from 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR' to 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Total time spent in 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR' across all cases
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR and the end of the case

Name: Average resolution time of 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR and the end of the case

Name: Minimum time from 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION' to 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Average time between 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR' and 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' for cases that are resubmitted
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR' and activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Total resolution time for cases involving 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR' and ending with 'Payment Handled'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR' and activity 'Payment Handled'

Name: Minimum time it takes from 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR' to the next 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR' and activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Average time from 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR' to 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION' in cases where the declaration is eventually approved
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR' and activity 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION'

Name: Total time for all activities between 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR' and 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR' and activity 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Average waiting time to 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR' from the start of the case
Metric: The average of the duration between the start of the case and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Average time it takes from 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR' to 'Request Payment' in cases that proceed to payment
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR' and activity 'Request Payment'

Name: Total time from 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR' to 'Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER' in cases involving pre-approval after rejection
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR' and activity 'Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER'

Name: Minimum resolution time of cases with 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR' that are successfully resolved
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR and the end of the case

Name: Average time from 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR' to case closure for cases that do not proceed to payment
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR' and the end of case where activity 'Request Payment does not occur
